  "title": "TEMP/PERM HR RECRUITMENT CONSULTANT #HGAT",
  "description": "<p>💡 What You’ll Be Doing:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Source, screen, and assess</strong> potential candidates for healthcare &amp; life sciences roles</li>\n  <li><strong>Coordinate and conduct interviews</strong>, assisting with hiring decisions</li>\n  <li>Build and maintain <strong>strong candidate relationships</strong> for future placements</li>\n  <li>Support HR-related processes such as <strong>offer management, onboarding</strong>, and talent tracking</li>\n  <li>Act as a trusted partner to clients, understanding their hiring needs and culture</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🎯 What We’re Looking For:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Diploma/degree</strong> in any field</li>\n  <li>Strong <strong>interpersonal and communication skills</strong></li>\n  <li>Willingness to learn, be coached, and grow</li>\n  <li><strong>No experience required</strong> – one to one mentorship &amp; hands-on training will be provided</li>\n  <li>Passion for working with people and making a difference in their careers</li>\n</ul>\n<p>🌟 What’s In It For You:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>Mentorship and structured training</strong> by senior consultants</li>\n  <li><strong>Collaborative team environment</strong></li>\n  <li>Opportunities to grow your <strong>HR, recruitment, and business development skills</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>📩 <strong>How to Apply:</strong></p>\n<p>Interested candidates can send your resume to:<br>\n💬 Telegram: @AnnGXT<br>\n📧 Email: <strong>anngoh@recruitexpress.com.sg</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ann Goh Xin Ting</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Recruit Express Pte Ltd<br>\nR1875289<br>\nE.A License: 99C4599</strong></p>",
